@HOST=http://localhost:4050/api
@TOKEN=YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE

### ℹ️ Perfil del Usuario Autenticado

### 📥 Obtener Perfil
GET {{HOST}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### 🔄 Actualizar Perfil
PUT {{HOST}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "firstSurname": "Doe",
  "birthdayDate": "1990-01-01"
}

### 🔐 Cambiar Contraseña
POST {{HOST}}/profile/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "current_password",
  "newPassword": "new_strong_password"
}
